arStrings.szText: {c_highlight}Mother's Gifts{/c} drop from slaying powerful enemies. The greater the challenge, the more you receive.
A new challenge awaits you in {c_highlight}World Tier 3{/c}. Gather the {c_highlight}Mother's Gift{/c} to build the strength to face the{icon:Marker_BSK_Entrance,2.5}{c_highlight}Infernal Hordes{/c}!
